video.title: Warehouse 13
video.synopsis: In this sci-fi show, Secret Service agents track down items missing from Warehouse 13, a top-secret facility where supernatural objects are stored.

episodes.synopsis: After saving the president's life, two Secret Service agents find themselves hastily transferred to Warehouse 13, a huge, top-secret storage facility.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka must stop a team of bank robbers who use an unusual weapon -- an unreleased pop song that mesmerizes those who hear it.
episodes.title: Resonance

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka are sent to a small town in upstate New York to investigate why the residents seem to be acting out their subconscious desires.
episodes.title: Magnetism

episodes.synopsis: Artie is kidnapped by a woman who believes that he was responsible for the death of her brother 12 years earlier.
episodes.title: Claudia

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka investigate when a sculpture is stolen thanks to a Native American artifact that let the thief walk through the steel walls of a vault.
episodes.title: Elements

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka must complete the life-threatening mission of a long-dead Warehouse agent who disappeared while on the hunt for an artifact.
episodes.title: Burnout

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka rejoin their Secret Service detail in Washington, D.C., to intercept a samurai sword about to be given to the president as a gift.
episodes.title: Implosion

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka are dispatched to Las Vegas to retrieve an artifact that seems to bestow good fortune on a couple of gamblers.
episodes.title: Duped

episodes.synopsis: When Artie gets wind of a rash of unexplained suicides at a Florida prison, he sends Pete and Myka to investigate.
episodes.title: Regrets

episodes.synopsis: The Regents question Artie while Pete, Myka and Claudia are trapped in the Warehouse, with energy levels reaching critical mass.
episodes.title: Breakdown

episodes.synopsis: After failing to catch MacPherson, Myka learns her dad is dying and heads home to see her parents -- only to find the situation worse than expected.
episodes.title: Nevermore

episodes.synopsis: Pete, Myka and Artie track down MacPherson after discovering that he's auctioning artifacts he's siphoned from the Warehouse shelves.
episodes.title: MacPherson

episodes.synopsis: MacPherson has blown Artie to smithereens and disappeared. Is Leena really a traitor? Where has Claudia gone.
episodes.title: Time Will Tell

episodes.synopsis: A masked vigilante with an artifact is cleaning up the mean streets of Detroit.
episodes.title: Mild Mannered

episodes.synopsis: When an artifact meant for the Warehouse turns up in the small town next door, the team finds themselves in the middle of a B-movie meltdown.
episodes.title: Beyond Our Control

episodes.synopsis: When young supermodels rapidly age 50 years overnight, Pete and Myka go undercover in the glam world of high fashion.
episodes.title: Age Before Beauty

episodes.synopsis: When the Warehouse orders a computer upgrade from Global Dynamics, EUREKA's Fargo comes to handle the install.
Pete and Myka are in the field, about to complete a mission, when Mrs. Frederic makes a surprise appearance.
episodes.title: Around the Bend

episodes.synopsis: Myka and Claudia investigate mysterious deaths on a college wrestling team, but they're shocked when an old foe shows up to help.
episodes.title: For the Team

episodes.synopsis: The Warehouse agents hope to spend a weekend just relaxing and being normal, but an artifact gets in the way.
episodes.title: Merge with Caution

episodes.synopsis: When someone uses artifacts from Artie's past to commit a series of murders, the team must fly to Russia to track down the killer.
episodes.title: Vendetta

episodes.synopsis: After former agent Rebecca reopens a Warehouse 13 cold case, Pete and Myka use H.G. Wells's time machine to travel back to the year 1961.
episodes.title: Where and When

episodes.synopsis: When Mrs. Frederic becomes mysteriously ill, Pete, Myka and H.G. race to long-lost Warehouse 2 in Egypt in an effort to save her.
episodes.title: Buried

episodes.synopsis: Following the devastating events at Warehouse 2, the team races to stop a new threat.
episodes.title: Reset

episodes.synopsis: As the Warehouse team prepares to celebrate the holidays in snowy South Dakota, Pete and Myka are called upon to hunt down a malevolent Santa Claus.
episodes.title: Secret Santa

episodes.synopsis: New agent Steve Jinks gets initiated on his first assignment and almost dies on the job; luckily, former Warehouse agent Myka steps in to save him.
episodes.title: The New Guy

episodes.synopsis: Witnesses in a murder trial are suddenly losing their memories. Pete and reinstated agent Myka must race against time to solve the case.
episodes.title: Trials

episodes.synopsis: Artie and Dr. Calder are reunited on a new case, but when the victims' DNA reveals a cyber matrix, Hugo Miller, Vanessa's ex, joins the investigation.
episodes.title: Love Sick

episodes.synopsis: Pete gets a visit from his ex-wife, who is in town to remarry. An artifact follows her on her wedding day, turning the bride into the Queen Bee.
episodes.title: Queen for a Day

episodes.synopsis: Three generations of Warehouse agents have failed to retrieve Joshua's Trumpet -- an artifact that vaporized three separate victims.
The Warehouse agents are called to a case that sees the return of Fargo, who is trapped in a video game modeled after the Warehouse.
episodes.title: Don't Hate the Player

episodes.synopsis: After a brief sighting, Myka turns to her old CIA team to help find Leo, the man who murdered her old partner, Sam.
episodes.title: Past Imperfect

episodes.synopsis: Attempting to save a group of regents, Artie and Myka find themselves trapped in a building that is disintegrating under the power of an artifact.
episodes.title: The 40th Floor

episodes.synopsis: With a flash and a zap, numerous people begin to disappear, leaving only a charcoal smudge behind.
episodes.title: Shadows

episodes.synopsis: With the number of crazed, shivering, ravenous people on the rise, Myka and Pete determine the artifact responsible is a 19th-century mason jar.
episodes.title: Insatiable

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka race to stop Sykes from using his own cache of artifacts to destroy them and the Warehouse. Part 1 of 2.
episodes.title: Emily Lake

episodes.synopsis: Pete and Myka race to stop Sykes from using his own cache of artifacts to destroy them and the Warehouse. Part 2 of 2.
episodes.title: Stand

episodes.synopsis: Pete Lattimer is hit in the head by an artifact and wakes up to a life where he was never born.
episodes.title: The Greatest Gift
